@startuml seq-scoring-cv

title Scoring IA, conversion et provisioning

actor Visiteur as V
participant "Portail" as Portal
participant "Trigger" as Trigger
participant "Service IA" as Queue
participant "API Groq" as Groq
database "Lead" as Lead
participant "Conversion" as Conv
participant "Provisioning" as Prov
actor Candidat as Cand

== 1. Dépôt du CV ==

V -> Portal : Soumettre CV
Portal -> Trigger : CV rattaché au Lead

== 2. Scoring IA ==

Trigger -> Queue : Lancer scoring
activate Queue
Queue -> Lead : Extraire texte du CV
Queue -> Groq : Analyser CV (LLaMA 3.3)
Groq --> Queue : Score + Recommandation
Queue -> Lead : Enregistrer score et analyse
deactivate Queue

alt Score > 15 (qualifié)

  == 3. Conversion ==

  Queue -> Conv : Convertir le Lead
  activate Conv
  Conv -> Lead : Créer Account + Contact + Opportunity
  deactivate Conv

  == 4. Création du compte portail ==

  Conv -> Prov : Créer compte candidat
  activate Prov
  Prov --> Cand : Email de bienvenue
  deactivate Prov

else Score ≤ 15 (non qualifié)

  Queue -> Lead : Statut = Refusée

end

@enduml
